在早期爬行動物之中，楊氏蜥算是中型物種，頭顱骨略小於7公分，完整身長大約接近現代的[[砂巨蜥|砂巨蜥]]<ref>Gow CE (1975), ''Palaeontologia africana''.</ref>。某些早期研究認為楊氏蜥等早期[[雙孔類|雙孔類]]爬行動物的頭顱骨具有高度可活動性<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://whyihatetheropods.blogspot.com/2010/11/new-paper-braincase-of-youngina.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708072747/http://whyihatetheropods.blogspot.com/2010/11/new-paper-braincase-of-youngina.html |archive-date=2011-07-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>Evans, S.E. 1980. The skull of a new eosuchian reptile from the Lower Jurassic of South Wales, Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society, 70:203-264. {{doi|10.1111/j.1096-3642.1980.tb00852.x}}</ref>；近年研究顯示，楊氏蜥的腦殼、[[顎骨|顎骨]]之間可能沒有可活動關節，類似現代[[喙頭蜥|喙頭蜥]]的頭顱骨<ref>Johnston, P 2010. The constrictor dorsalis musculature and basipterygoid articulation in Sphenodon. Journal of Morphology. {{doi|10.1002/jmor.10797}}</ref>。

